  "content": "# M1.2 LiteStore Implementation Plan\n\n## Task 1: Config — Add StoreType and InferenceProvider Enums\n\n**Files:**\n- Modify: `crates/corvia-common/src/config.rs`\n\nThis task adds the enum types that distinguish LiteStore from SurrealDB, and Ollama from vLLM. Default flips from SurrealDB/vLLM to Lite/Ollama. SurrealDB config fields become `Option<String>` since they're unused in lite mode.\n",
